The paper investigates the performance of a massive MIMO system, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The use of precoded QPSK transmission also suggests a focus on signal processing (cs.SY) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper may also be relevant to communication and information theory (cs.COM) due to its investigation of channel capacity.
